  <h2>About Us</h2>
  <p>Hi, I’m the founder of Gard’s Company — a small, independent team based in Great Britain. We specialize in helping other small businesses grow by building strong, simple, and modern digital brands. From clean websites to social media strategy, we’re here to make your online presence work harder for you.</p>
</section>
- **Services:** <section>
  <h2>What We Offer</h2>
  <p>At Gard’s Company, we provide high-quality photography services tailored to your brand or personal style. Whether you're building a business, launching a product, or capturing a moment — we’re here to make it look stunning.</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Brand & Business Photography</li>
    <li>Product & Commercial Shoots</li>
